data.title: Capricorn Life Sciences
data.meta_description:
Capricorn Life Sciences | 298 followers on LinkedIn. Capricorn Life Sciences is your partner for pharmaceutical products with a story  | Capricorn Life Sciences is a trusted provider of unique, high quality products to many healthcare companies around the world. Our product portfolio of Food Supplements, FSMP’s and medical devices covers a broad range of therapeutic indications, including: 
1. gynecology/women’s health, 
2. gastroenterology, 
3. pediatrics, 
4. orthopedics, 
5. neurology, 
6. immunology, 
7. CNS and 
8. respiratory.
